    "body": "A bit of technical context:\r\n\r\nThe line below is the bug in the mobile code. https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/blob/a2bf23cc1281fa10a5b44e65c4cf41c2efeda293/src/status_im/contexts/communities/overview/view.cljs#L183\r\n\r\nThe logic to decide if we show permissions to join on the Community Overview screen should be based only on membership permissions. We should probably have a separate subscription, for example `:community/membership-permissions?`, so that we keep the view simple.\r\n\r\ncc @FFFra ",
